9. Algorithm
Start the program.
Display a welcome message.
Use an infinite loop for conversation.
Take user input.
Convert input to lowercase for easy comparison.
Check user input using conditional statements:
Greeting
Questions
Exit command
Display appropriate chatbot response.
If the user enters "exit":
Stop the loop.
End the program.
10. Sample Output
Bot: Hello! I am your chatbot.
You: hi

Bot: Hello! How can I help you?

You: what is your name?

Bot: I am a Python Chatbot.

You: bye

Bot: Goodbye!
